{"word":"Μόρυχος","slug":"Μόρυχος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n68787\" key=\"*mo/ruxos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Μόρῠχος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, epith. of dionysus in Sicily, from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μορύσσω</foreign>, because his face was <sense id=\"n68787.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">smeared</tr_> with wine lees at the vintage: prov., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μωρότερος Μορύχου</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0524.tlg001:94\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Sophr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">94</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n68787.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> only in <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μορυχώτερον</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">more obscurely</tr_>, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> l. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg025.perseus-grc1:987a:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Metaph.\">Metaph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">987a10</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alex.Aphr.</author> </bibl> ad <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10</biblScope> </bibl> c.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}